3. cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics): The problem of group testing involves combinatorial and discrete mathematics concepts such as set theory and graph theory. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper proposes a search procedure for detecting defective members, which falls under the scope of artificial intelligence.
